OL,5, A book-loving five-year-old has brought
OL,6, joy to care home residents by reading  
OL,7, his favourite stories to them.         
OL,9,FHarri, five, spends his free time after
OL,10,Fschool reading to residents in Pendine 
OL,11,FPark's Highfield care home in Wrexham. 
OL,13,FHis mum Laura said it was his love of  
OL,14,Freading that inspired her to bring the 
OL,15,Fbook fanatic to the care home where she
OL,16,Fworks.                                 
OL,18,FHarri has become a firm favourite among
OL,19,Fresidents and his mum said their faces 
OL,20,F"light up" when he arrives.            
